item.description:

mrtony:

plz help me i dont know if the people can log in on my server by using moparisthebest.com ??? and can they log in on my router ip adress ??? if no … can you help me i dont know how to make a loader and its too wtf for me ok ???

First off, your server needs to be configured to work with certain clients. Second, what revision is it? P.S. I wouldn’t recommend mopars client if you are trying to make a big server as it won’t have any custom items or godswords and such.
